description:
Florida Governor DeSantis pushes back on men competing with women in the NCAA. DeSantis declares the runner-up, a native of his state, the winner against transgender swimmer Lia Thomas. The party of science refuses to acknowledge biology. Despite being double vaxxed and boosted, White House press secretary Jen Psaki tests positive for covid for the second time since October. C&B steak dinner bet: Will Hunter Biden be indicted? British author JK Rowling is fearless on women's rights. Boston Mayor Michelle Wu failed joke: "I’m getting used to dealing with problems that are expensive, disruptive and white." No matter who the Republicans nominate in 2024, the media with say "Worse than Trump!" Including Trump!
